<h2>Fall 2016 Semiannual Report to Congress</h2>


<p>This fall edition of the <em>Semiannual Report to Congress</em> covers OIG activities from April 2016 through September 2016. Historically, about 80 percent of OIG's resources are directed to work related to Medicare and Medicaid. This is mirrored in the organization and content of the report.</p>

